block content
  section.bucket.content
    h1.bucket__title Mon bucket

    if flash && flash.success && flash.success.length
      aside.alert-success
        ul
          each i in flash.success
            li= flash.success.shift()
        a.

    p.bucket_description
      | My soul felt so safe up here, no self-centered natives destroying our Earth.
      | I am sane! I don't understand a word you're sayin'! ...there's another case study for anthropology.
      | I ain't sayin' anything that could be construed as an apology...